name: Listened to Canes Confidential: The culture change under Mario Cristobal

content.html:
As Miami works its way through two-third of spring practice, Manny is back to talk about what’s transpired from a culture perspective with the Hurricanes under Mario Cristobal, transfers, recruiting and where the Canes remain deficient from a roster perspective. Carlos Ledo of the MIA All Day Podcast is along again for the ride, which includes answering some mailbag questions. Learn more about your ad choices. Visit megaphone.fm/adchoices

By Wide Right: A show about the Miami Hurricanes
